cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.PL, cs.RO 

This paper discusses the use of reinforcement learning towards achieving strong-AI, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also utilizes elements of programming languages (cs.PL) and robotics (cs.RO) to restructure the reinforcement learning algorithm. Additionally, the paper discusses the Game Of Giving and Asking For Reasons, which relates to computational complexity (cs.CC).
